 11222</p></a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="mailto:hello@bolt.build">hello@bolt.build</a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="tel:+1 917-740-3463">+1 917-740-3463</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 border-t-0 lg:border-t border-x md:border-x-0 border-current"></div></div></div><div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10"><div class="cover-image-shim absolute inset-0 z-10"></div><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Ff4041dab58c157cbbcfe81f7979daa55a59e4d3d-1920x1080.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Ff4041dab58c157cbbcfe81f7979daa55a59e4d3d-1920x1080.png&w=1920&q=75amp;qhttps://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Ff4041dab58c157cbbcfe81f7979daa55a59e4d3d-1920x1080.png&w=3840&q=75;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="absolute object-cover w-full h-full z-0 inset-0" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 300vw, (max-width: 1000px) 200vw, 100vw"/></div><div class="border-x flex-1 flex flex-col justify-end"></div></header><div class="z-20 relative bg-white"><div class="sticky top-0 invisible"><div class="px-unit absolute left-0 right-0 bg-white"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-b"></div></div></div><div class="px-unit"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-x"><div class="sticky top-unit"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-2 pb-4"><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-3 pr-2"><p class="text-current font-body text-3xl">Client Spotlight | Soft Bar </p></div><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-2"><h3 class="text-current font-body text-md">September 2, 2025</h3></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-8 pb-unit"><div class="col-start-1 col-end-13 md:col-start-2 md:col-end-12 lg:col-start-4 lg:col-end-12 xl:col-start-4 xl:col-end-10"><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Bolt Builds has been working with Carl Radke to bring his new project to life as a first-of-its-kind non-alcoholic bar and café focused on mindful and delicious consumption. The Summer House personality has been very candid and open about his five year long sobriety journey and is dedicated to helping others live a healthier lifestyle, which has led him to his calling of opening Soft Bar.</p><div class="mt-12 mb-8 w-full"><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F9b012356df9e1359a05fac1b27501340dd583178-1080x1350.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F9b012356df9e1359a05fac1b27501340dd583178-1080x1350.png&w=1080&q=75amp;qhttps://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F9b012356df9e1359a05fac1b27501340dd583178-1080x1350.png&w=3840&q=75;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" alt="soft bar material" width="1080" height="1350" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Carl explains “I was looking for something that feels and looks like the other cool and elevated spots, but most of those places are very limited in their non-alc options. I don&#x27;t drink alcohol and I don&#x27;t drink coffee, so I don&#x27;t exist in New York City.&quot;</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Typical NA spaces are sterile, either with no space to enjoy beverages or limited hours. With 38% of Americans who choose not to drink alcohol and many consciously shifting away from sugary mocktails, Soft Bar aims to be a space for everyone to exist. The menu will feature soft cocktails and functional drinks that naturally enhance well-being, perfect for anyone looking to sip and socialize or enjoy a drink with added benefits.</p><div class="mt-12 mb-8 w-full"><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Fb31ce3a05b109e79cad2b83b6b80f63a50a32cf9-1080x1437.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Fb31ce3a05b109e79cad2b83b6b80f63a50a32cf9-1080x1437.jpg&w=1080&q=75amp;qhttps://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Fb31ce3a05b109e79cad2b83b6b80f63a50a32cf9-1080x1437.jpg&w=3840&q=75;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" alt="soft bar" width="1080" height="1437" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Radke’s vision includes a morning café featuring local coffee roasters, a daytime workspace/creative studio, an evening bar and an event space with fitness leaders, gatherings, and music—amplified with community and meaningful connections. Bolt’s focus is to create an all encompassing third-space that can evolve to embrace all these facets.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><div class="mt-12 mb-8 w-full"><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Fbcddbc60824c4c3b3959e4bccf250802a8967153-1080x1440.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Fbcddbc60824c4c3b3959e4bccf250802a8967153-1080x1440.jpg&w=1080&q=75amp;qhttps://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2Fbcddbc60824c4c3b3959e4bccf250802a8967153-1080x1440.jpg&w=3840&q=75;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" alt="soft bar" width="1080" height="1440" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">The 2,300 SF space in Greenpoint is a former industrial garage with exposed brick and concrete floors, which will be enhanced by an infinite bar and a glass facade. The space is designed to emphasize natural materials, calming lighting, and a cozy, mindful atmosphere. The color palette features soothing naturals, warm neutrals, and muted dark pastels. Soft wood fixtures and plush furniture offset the industrial shell, while luxurious stone accents and clean lines bring the space together.</p><div class="mt-16"><div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-6 pb-8"><div><p class="text-current font-body text-xl text-black mx-auto text-center max-w-[420px]">Subscribe to our newsletter to get the latest updates, insights, and articles from our team.</p><div class="mt-4 text-center"><div class="border-black border inline-block"><form class="flex items-center justify-between"><input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="bg-white px-5 py-4 rounded-none focus:outline-none hover:bg-diminished flex-1" value=""/><button type="submit" class="min-w-[160px] px-5 py-4 bg-black text-white hover:bg-blue transition-colors">Subscribe</button></form></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-8 pb-unit flex justify-between"><a class="col-span-3 hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity" href="../insights"><p class="text-current font-body text-md">Return to Insights List</p><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">←</p></a><a class="col-start-10 col-span-3 text-right hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity" href="breeze-blocks"><p class="text-current font-body text-md">Next Insight</p><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">Matter of Design | Breeze Blocks <!-- --> →</p></a></div></div></div><footer class="bg-white pb-unit px-unit relative z-[1000]"><div class="bg-white border border-b border-black pt-unit pb-unit"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit"><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-3"><a class="text-current hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="../index.html"><div class="w-[24px]"><div class="w-full "><svg width="100